{"tid":2051552,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【別讓「重慶」李嘉誠跑了】簽名撐國安法 張松橋清空中國資產 200億押注英澳","createTime":"2020-06-05T01:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T04:28:04.000Z","uid":130626,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7c62006eea1d197247f1062d224607a543c9fa45","tid":2051552,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T01:01:25.000Z","msg":"早前政府將持續進修基金加碼，每位市民最多獲二萬元資助，今年起更獨家將駕駛課程納入資助範圍，獨家資助市民在香港駕駛學院學車，計劃一出現時額滿。運輸署早前已增發226個教車師傅牌，特別優待香港駕駛學院，令其進一步壟斷市場，大批師傅怨聲載道。<br />\n<br />\n香港駕駛學院是港股控股旗下，大股東是有「重慶李嘉誠」之稱的張松橋。他行蹤神秘，甚少在媒體前出現，地位及身家雖未達到「李嘉誠」級數，但持有西隧、大老山隧道、香港駕駛學院以及道路繳費系統「快易通」等，可謂掌控全港的交通命脈。大部份香港人，都要俾錢他賺，一年收入逾25億元。<br />\n<br />\n不過，本刊發現袋了香港人錢的張松橋，另一邊廂，卻「走資」去英澳。他旗下的中渝置地（1224），過去四年套現國內項目共159億元，而過去兩年內買入英澳資產共228億元。這間所謂的「內房」公司，實際已是「外房」。一邊簽名支持「國安法」的他，卻似乎與香港市民一樣，對香港及內地出現信心危機。<br />\n全文Link<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_743780_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_743780_0&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=37e53976\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_743780_0&h=3f56bd11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_743780_0</a>"},{"pid":"4bfd8fb87b0d44290bf57b57e0e3bd1f77a9b83a","tid":2051552,"uid":21661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T01:08:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e69382f06866d18842d9c708235f7890845bd7","tid":2051552,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T01:10:03.000Z","msg":"連登仔：誠哥都係賣中環中心咋，咁都叫走資？"},{"pid":"a99a9cbb974326e1956cd16c169d276247e40406","tid":2051552,"uid":324163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T01:10:19.000Z","msg":"鬥紅啊嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2a934d763d8942c113e1fc3b1f5d1d6d548b74","tid":2051552,"uid":264074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T01:27:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />賣國賊！！！漢奸！！！"},{"pid":"930b1f1fc01b61556565ae90ca004e5e6f404bf8","tid":2051552,"uid":61589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"80e69382f06866d18842d9c708235f7890845bd7","tid":2051552,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T01:10:03.000Z","msg":"連登仔：誠哥都係賣中環中心咋，咁都叫走資？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:15:29.000Z","msg":"賣緊PCCW喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0baaca0fbf6089ef6bd77ca34d2cf62d17477d94","tid":2051552,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:16:59.000Z","msg":"港豬：唔怕！全族身家入市買樓, 龍市GO GO GO"},{"pid":"59a2ca60414f01edf2fec26ac4b90e9eace9e16d","tid":2051552,"uid":231724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:17:13.000Z","msg":"惡意走資，拉"},{"pid":"be1617772792fda200481583de51204466694a71","tid":2051552,"uid":150014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:17:22.000Z","msg":"你估佢唔驚比人拉食晒副身家咩？<br />\n而家仲點會返嚟"},{"pid":"872e6f8d0b7aa681d1d353ce39aade8aea3ff9bd","tid":2051552,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:25:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d9722df5e9c5d85e2d7b51d816f3a5754b1b2053","tid":2051552,"uid":248299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0baaca0fbf6089ef6bd77ca34d2cf62d17477d94","tid":2051552,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:16:59.000Z","msg":"港豬：唔怕！全族身家入市買樓, 龍市GO GO GO"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:28:04.000Z","msg":"：邊度走資 股市日日升"}]}